description:
&lt;p&gt;Are you a skilled secretary? Would you like the opportunity to work in a fast paced team in a varied adminstrative role?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a candidate motivated and willing to develop within our current small expert team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We offer a variety of roles, so whether you are just starting out in your career or you are looking to use your skills and experience in a new role. The post holder will provide and coordinate administrative services; including preparing patient records, carrying out medical transcriptionsas well as gathering information and arranging meetings as and when necessary for the team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will need to be a flexible and motivated individual who is capable of working as part of a friendly, hard-working team. You must have excellent communication skills, plus be able to embrace the constant fast pace within the department. If you are adaptable to change and like to be active, this is the job for you.&lt;/p&gt;
